      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nItem-level spend from FIS STDFSID (Filtered Spend Item Details) XTRACT v1.3.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| UPC | `fact_spend_item_detail.upc` | Product barcode |\n| Item Description | `fact_spend_item_detail.item_description` | Product name |\n| Spend Category | `fact_spend_item_detail.spend_category_code` | 5D=Food, 5A=OTC, OF/OV=OTC variants |\n| Item Amount | `fact_spend_item_detail.item_amount` | Line item dollar amount |\n| Item Quantity | `fact_spend_item_detail.item_quantity` | Units purchased |\n| Is Funded | `fact_spend_item_detail.is_funded` | Whether the item was funded by the benefit |\n| Merchant | `fact_spend_item.merchant_name` | Store where purchased |\n| Settle Amount | `fact_spend_item.settle_amount` | Total transaction amount |\n\n> **393 items** across **99 transactions** from ~60% of RFU members.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
